      <title>新日铁聘请蓬佩奥协助完成对美国钢铁公司的收购</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/nippon-steel-hires-pompeo-to-help-clinch-purchase-of-us-steel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新日铁公司已聘请美国前国务卿迈克·蓬佩奥协助完成对美国钢铁公司的收购提议，该交易遭到唐纳德·特朗普和总统乔·拜登的两党反对。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/nippon-steel-hires-pompeo-to-help-clinch-purchase-of-us-steel</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 18:29:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙与中右翼联手对抗左翼，争夺议会职位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/macron-center-right-join-forces-against-left-in-parliament-jobs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙的政治团体与法国国民议会的中右翼议员达成了权力分享协议，这是他可能试图组建一个排除左翼和右翼激进政党的中间派联合政府的最新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/macron-center-right-join-forces-against-left-in-parliament-jobs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 17:49:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管软件延迟，洛克希德仍恢复 F-35 战斗机交付</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/lockheed-resumes-f-35-jet-deliveries-despite-software-delays</link>
      <description><![CDATA[五角大楼决定不再等待被推迟的硬件和软件升级，从而恢复向洛克希德·马丁公司付款，并接收了首架 F-35 战斗机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/lockheed-resumes-f-35-jet-deliveries-despite-software-delays</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 17:23:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约州称预计三年预算缺口将缩减 62 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/ny-state-three-year-budget-gap-shrinks-by-6-2-billion-dinapoli</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约州审计长托马斯·迪纳波利表示，由于国民经济走强和工资增长带来税收增长，纽约州三年预算缺口累计达到 139 亿美元，比州长凯西·霍楚尔二月份的估计下降了 60 多亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/ny-state-three-year-budget-gap-shrinks-by-6-2-billion-dinapoli</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 16:57:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>迈克·诺沃格拉茨是推动拜登继任计划的危险捐助者之一</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/novogratz-pushes-democrats-to-adopt-risky-plan-to-replace-biden</link>
      <description><![CDATA[希望取代总统乔·拜登成为候选人的民主党捐助者主张通过公开的选拔程序来寻找替代方案，这一策略充满政治风险和后勤未知数。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/novogratz-pushes-democrats-to-adopt-risky-plan-to-replace-biden</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 16:15:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国际货币基金组织称赞比亚的去美元化计划可能无效</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/imf-says-zambia-s-dedollarization-plan-may-be-counterproductive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际货币基金组织表示，赞比亚提议禁止在当地交易中使用外币，违者将被判处 10 年监禁，但这一禁令可能会适得其反。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/imf-says-zambia-s-dedollarization-plan-may-be-counterproductive</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 11:33:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
